makeup.name: Nykaa Get Cheeky! Blush Duo Palette - Brazilian Bombshell 01
makeup.des: It's time to play naughty and nice with Nykaa Get Cheeky Blush Duo. This blush duo brings a natural-looking flush of color that pops on every skin tone. This palette provides a dominant color and a subtle color for blending and softening edges. Infused with radiance-boosting minerals, These pigments sweep on weightless, And a soft veil of color. The ultra-light, Micronized pigments of these shades blend effortlessly into the skin and give you a buildable coverage to enhance the apples of your cheeks!

makeup.name: Kay Beauty Creme Blush - Cosy Coral
makeup.des: The Kay Beauty Creme Blush is a highly pigmented formula that delivers a glowy flush to your cheeks. Its mousse-like texture blends seamlessly without streaking or caking. Easy to blend, easy to build, and easy to use, you can work this lightweight blush with your fingertips to create a natural sun-kissed finish. All you have to do is dab, blend and go from a soft daytime finish to a glam night out look.

makeup.name: Maybelline New York Fit Me Mono Blush - 20 Hopeful
makeup.des: Explore the entire range of Blush available on Nykaa. Shop more Maybelline New York products here.You can browse through the complete world of Maybelline New York Blush.Alternatively, you can also find many more products from the Maybelline New York Fit Me Mono Blush range.

makeup.name: Charmacy Milano Cheek Enhancer - 4
makeup.des: Glow naturally with Charmacy Milano Cheek Enhancer - a powder blush that helps you achieve that lit-from-within look. Suitable for all skin types, it has a true-to-tone colour and provides great colour pay-off. Take your pick from 4 highly pigmented shades. Its silky and lightweight texture is highly buildable and blendable, and looks freshly applied all day long.

makeup.name: Love Earth Multipot-Be The Change Lip Tint with Jojoba Oil and Vitamin E for Lips Eyelids & Cheeks
makeup.des: Love Earth Multipot-Be The Change is a multipurpose product that works as a tint and moisturizes your lips as well. It has nourishing and hydrating properties as well. It can be used on your lips, cheeks and eyelids for a flush of colour. This product is made with natural ingredients that will be giving you that fierce nutritive benefits to the innermost layers of your skin. It feels super light and keeps your skin moisturized all day long.

makeup.name: Swiss Beauty Lip & Cheek Cream - Cinnamon
makeup.des: Swiss Beauty Lip & Cheek Cream multitasks! You and can give your lips cheek or eyelids a tint along with long lasting moisture .it is super light,with goodness of vitamin E and olive oil, to give you a natural fresh and glowing look all day long.

makeup.name: Makeup Revolution Superdewy Liquid Blusher You Had Me At First Blush(15ml)
makeup.des: Add a hint of tint to your look with the Makeup Revolution Superdewy Liquid Blush. An easy to use, ultra-pigmented, buildable liquid blush. Go for a natural flushed finish or build it up for a more pigmented look with Makeup Revolution Superdewy Liquid Blush.

makeup.name: Charlotte Tilbury Pillow Talk Lip And Cheek Glow - Colour Of Dreams
makeup.des: Inspired by the best-selling, award-winning world of Pillow Talk and the youthful, playful colours of love, dreams and passion, these radiant, emollient-rich lip and cheek glow creams deliver a look of just-kissed, meadow-fresh, semi-sheer colour to the lips and cheeks, so you can be your most beautiful you!

makeup.name: Bobbi Brown Pot Rouge For Lips & Cheeks - Powder Pink(3.7g)
makeup.des: Bobbi Brown's best-selling, multitasking cream color for lips and cheeks comes in a mirrored flip-top compact for on-the-spot application.

makeup.name: Flower Beauty Blush Bomb Color Drops - Nectar
makeup.des: A new way to give your cheeks a fresh healthy glow in an instant! Introducing Flower Beauty Blush Bomb Color Drops, a collection of heart pumping blush shades guaranteed to turn up the volume on your makeup look. Each drop of this silky, lightweight formula blends seamlessly for a perfect flush every time. It has a buildable and natural looking formula.

makeup.name: Benefit Cosmetics GoGo Tint
makeup.des: Gogotint is the wildest flush you can get from a bottle! This see-through bright cherry red lip & cheek stain is vibrant, juicy and pops till you drop. Release your inner rebel with colour that lasts!

makeup.name: Daughter Earth 100% Vegan, Vitamin - E Lip And Cheek Tint
makeup.des: Daughter Earth Lip & Cheek Tint is a 100% vegan and nutri-active, vitamin E enriched lip and cheek colour. It is clean, safe and kind to your skin. This pigmented formula gives your lips and cheeks a naturally flushed look. What's better? The brand did so by choosing vegan, clean and kind ingredient alternatives.

makeup.name: Benefit Cosmetics ChaCha Tint
makeup.des: This mango-tinted stain beautifully blushes lips & cheeks with a tropical coral hue. Smooch-proof & smudge-proof, our sheer stain has a natural finish that will leave you looking deliciously vibrant for hours.

makeup.name: SUGAR Air Kiss Powder Lipstick - 04 Cherry Fluff
makeup.des: Experience what magic feels like on your lips with India’s 1st ever SUGAR Air Kiss Powder Lipstick. Yes, you read that right! This unique lipstick with a breakthrough powder formula magically melts into a slick matte finish when applied. It leaves behind a bold burst of colour that stays put for hours without any streaks. Ultra-lightweight and non-drying, it dries off within seconds and settles to a smooth texture that is transfer-proof and water-resistant.

makeup.name: Flower Beauty Blush Bomb Color Drops - Nectar
makeup.des: A new way to give your cheeks a fresh healthy glow in an instant! Introducing Flower Beauty Blush Bomb Color Drops, a collection of heart pumping blush shades guaranteed to turn up the volume on your makeup look. Each drop of this silky, lightweight formula blends seamlessly for a perfect flush every time. It has a buildable and natural looking formula.

makeup.name: Renee Cosmetics Lip & Cheek Tint - Red Romance
makeup.des: Looking for the magical spell that sets everything alright? Well, Renee's all new Lip and Cheek Tint is that exact secret magic potion packed inside a box. With an alluring shade that can be used for your lips, cheeks and your eyelids, this product is all set to pave its way to your heart.

makeup.name: Nykaa Glow Goals! Shimmer Brick Highlighter Palette - Shimmer Rays
makeup.des: Nykaa Glow Goals! Shimmer Brick Highlighter Palette - Shimmer Rays

makeup.name: Nudestix Nudies Blush All Over Face Color - Bare Back
makeup.des: Nudestix Nudies Blush All-Over Face Color is a multi-tasking balm to offer warm bronze and romantic blush tones on your face, eyes and lips for an easy #gonudebutbetter look. Convenient removable blending brush for applying on-the-go!

makeup.name: Kay Beauty Contour & Highlight Pro Palette - Contour Genius
makeup.des: Define your features like a pro with the Kay Beauty Contour & Highlight Pro Palette that sculpts your face with its high-definition powder matte formula. The all-in-one kit offers three universal shades in a warm tone, cool tone and neutral tone to help you create your own shade that's a perfect match for your skin tone. Its feathery lightweight feel and premium texture allows for beautiful blending and HD contouring that can be built from subtle definition to chiseled cheekbones. This high hydration formula lets you bronze, contour and highlight in one go without the hassle of using multiple products. It’s incredibly long lasting, sweat and water resistant too so no need for constant touch-ups. Get ready to carve out that killer bone structure with minimal effort.

makeup.name: Huda Beauty Glowish Soft Radiance Bronzing Powder Mini - 02 Medium
makeup.des: The same velvety bronzing powder, now with three shades available in mini size!
